Package: jaspatial
Type: Package
Title: Make Spatial Analysis Easier For JA Employees
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("David", "McClendon", email="david@januaryadvisors.com", role="aut")
Maintainer: David McClendon <david@januaryadvisors.com>
Description: This package sets up your environment for spatial analysis and mapping  
    by loading a suite of R packages and setting options appropriately.
    It also includes a number of custom functions for spatial analysis that we 
    use frequently in our work.
